Just an example of meteor application

Using this meteor packages

accounts-password   1.0.5  Password support for accounts
accounts-ui         1.1.4  Simple templates to add login widgets to an app
cwohlman:pickadate  1.0.0  The mobile-friendly, responsive, and lightweight jQuery date & time input picker.
meteor-platform     1.2.1  Include a standard set of Meteor packages in your app
numeral:numeral     1.5.3  Numeral.js (official) - formatting and manipulating numbers.
twbs:bootstrap      3.3.1_2  Bootstrap (official): the most popular HTML/CSS/JS framework for responsive, mobile first projects
wollardj:timeago    1.0.1  Meteor wrapper for the momentjs fromNow() method.
